ndreds of millions of years since its birth. It\u2019s occasionally found during the excavation of caves."}, {"version": "moon", "text": "Although this Pok\u00e9mon is not especially rare, its glittering, jewel-draped body draws attention from people."}, {"version": "omega-ruby", "text": "Born from the temperatures and pressures deep underground, it fires beams from the stone in its head."}, {"version": "shield", "text": "It\u2019s said that somewhere in the world, there\u2019s a mineral vein housing a large pack of slumbering Carbink. It\u2019s also said that this pack has a queen."}, {"version": "sun", "text": "Born from the high temperatures and pressures deep underground, it defends itself by firing beams from the jewel part of its body."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "When beset by attackers, Carbink wipes them all out by firing high-energy beams from the gems embedded in its body."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "To keep the jewels on their bodies free of tarnish, packs of Carbink use their soft manes to polish one another\u2019s jewels."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "Some say that deep beneath the surface of the world, a pack of Carbink live with their queen in a kingdom of jewels."}, {"version": "x", "text": "Born from the temperatures and pressures deep underground, it fires beams from the stone in its head."}, {"version": "y", "text": "It has slept underground for hundreds of millions of years since its birth. It\u2019s occasionally found during the excavation of caves."}], "entryGameVersions": ["alpha-sapphire", "moon", "omega-ruby", "shield", "sun", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun", "x", "y"], "moveGameGroups": ["omega-ruby-alpha-sapphire", "scarlet-violet", "sun-moon", "sword-shield", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon", "x-y"], "evolutionRows": [{"stage": 1, "name": "carbink"}]}